            {
              "id": "b98f3257-b380-4d33-b26b-134fdcd47081",
              "content": "<p>Integration ran manually Thursday, May 14 and trigger set</p>"
            },
            {
              "id": "d4a23bf7-a732-46a3-a447-f439653dec52",
              "content": "<p>Live integration ran Friday, May 15 without issues</p>"
            },
            {
              "id": "425c84c5-96d4-4067-9442-8004362f6789",
              "content": "<p><strong>Integration Details:</strong></p><ul><li>City IT (Harrison) has a cleanup script that runs each morning at 3:00am to archive the previous day's file (to prevent duplicate ingestion)</li><li>The integration file from the Court is sent to the server Axon has access to at 3:15am</li><li>Axon picks up the file at 5:00am</li><li>Records team begins working the warrants at 6:00am</li></ul>"
            }
          ]
        },
